# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GoHenry .gitignore — keeps secrets and build junk out of the public repo.
# (Comments must be on their own line; Git does NOT support inline comments.)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Secrets / machine-local config (NEVER commit to a public repo) ---
# Azure Functions: connection strings, storage keys, Key Vault refs
local.settings.json
# Android SDK path (machine-specific)
local.properties
# Firebase config — each developer brings their own before building
**/google-services.json
*.keystore
*.jks
.env
.env.*
secrets.json

# --- .NET / Azure Functions build output ---
**/bin/
**/obj/
*.user

# --- Android / Gradle build output ---
.gradle/
**/build/
*.iml
captures/
.cxx/

# --- IDE / editor ---
.idea/
.vs/
.vscode/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
